    "When it is conducted remotely, the evaluator can follow the study synchronously or asynchronously and is mediated by ad-hoc tools [32,43,52,102].",
    "The remote usability testing is most relevant for HCAI systems designed for large-scale or cross-cultural use where users might be placed worldwide.",
